msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/date"
msgid "March 10th, 1945 · East of Lake Balaton, Hungary"
msgstr "10 de marzo de 1945 - Al este del lago Balaton, Hungría"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/name"
msgid "The Final Offensive <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"
msgstr "La última ofensiva <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/name_big"
msgid "The Final Offensive"
msgstr "La última ofensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/01"
msgid ""
"Soldaten! We have a task of strategic importance ahead! Our forces are "
"conducting a counteroffensive codenamed \"Spring Awakening\"."
msgstr ""
"¡Soldados! ¡Tenemos una tarea de importancia estratégica! Nuestras fuerzas "
"están llevando a cabo una contraofensiva bajo el nombre de \"Despertar de "
"Primavera\"."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/02"
msgid ""
"The soviet forces are well entrenched, and maybe they outnumber us, but "
"today we have the latest armour and weaponry at our disposal. The bolshevik "
"armor will be no match for our Königstigers."
msgstr ""
"Las fuerzas soviéticas están bien atrincheradas, y tal vez nos superen en "
"número, pero hoy disponemos de lo último en blindaje y armamento. Los "
"tanques bolcheviques no será rival para nuestros Königstigers."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/03"
msgid ""
"We are low on supplies. You are to seize the key depots of this area first. "
"Watch out for enemy aviation."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos pocos suministros. Primero debes priorizar capturar los depósitos "
"clave de esta zona. Tened cuidado con la posible aparición de aviación "
"enemiga."

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/04"
msgid ""
"Good job! Our reinforcements will be arriving shortly from the south west."
msgstr "¡Buen trabajo! Nuestros refuerzos llegarán en breve desde el suroeste."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/05"
msgid ""
"Excellent work! There are some supply vehicles here, maybe they have some of "
"our ammunition we can take back."
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo! Hay algunos vehículos de suministro por aquí, tal vez "
"tengan algo de nuestra munición que nos pueda servir."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/06"
msgid ""
"Finally! Some much needed fuel is at our disposal. Let's make the most out "
"of this trophy."
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! Ahora disponemos de un combustible muy necesario. Aprovechemos al "
"máximo este trofeo."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/07"
msgid ""
"This workshop contains all the tools we need if we run our of our own repair "
"tools. Let's scavenge all we can find."
msgstr ""
"Este taller contiene todas las herramientas que necesitamos si nos quedamos "
"sin nuestras piezas de recambio. Busquemos todo lo que podamos encontrar."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/08"
msgid ""
"The enemy HQ is taken out! We have taken a huge leap forward in this fight. "
"In case the enemy counter-attacks, you should get ready!"
msgstr ""
"¡El cuartel general enemigo ha sido silenciado! Hemos dado un gran paso "
"adelante en esta lucha. En caso de que el enemigo contraataque, ¡debes estar "
"preparado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/09"
msgid ""
"Good work Soldiers. We've managed to drive out the enemy from all the key "
"objectives. Unfortunately, we don't have the fuel for a next offensive move."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, soldados. Hemos conseguido expulsar al enemigo de todos los "
"objetivos clave. Desafortunadamente, el resto de las divisiones no tienen el "
"combustible necesario para continuar con la ofensiva."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/10"
msgid ""
"We've been ordered to take all the valuable supplies and hold off any Soviet "
"counterattacks. Our original starting position cannot fall to the enemy "
"under any circumstance!"
msgstr ""
"Se nos ha ordenado recoger todos los suministros valiosos, replegarnos y "
"detener cualquier contraataque soviético. ¡Nuestra posición inicial no puede "
"caer en manos del enemigo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/11"
msgid ""
"You are given command of our heaviest and most devastating weapon: the "
"Jagdtiger. Blow those Soviet tanks to bits!"
msgstr ""
"Se te ha dado el mando de nuestra bestia más pesada y devastadora: el "
"Jagdtiger. ¡Vuela en pedazos esos tanques soviéticos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/12"
msgid ""
"Damn it! Soviet troops are already entering our starting positions! Clear "
"the area immediately!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea! ¡Las tropas soviéticas están muy cerca! ¡Despejad el área "
"inmediatamente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/13"
msgid ""
"Excellent work, Soldaten! Once again you have made the Fatherland proud. "
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo, soldados! Una vez más habéis hecho que nuestra patria se "
"sienta orgullosa."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/14"
msgid ""
"Look, a damaged soviet tank stranded in the swamp... I suppose we could use "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Mira, un tanque soviético dañado varado en el pantano... Supongo que "
"podríamos repararlo…"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/narrator/officer/15"
msgid "A T-34 has been ditched in the swamp. I bet we can get it repaired!"
msgstr ""
"Un T-34 ha sido abandonado en el pantano. ¡Apuesto a que podemos repararlo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Well done! You accomplished about everything there was to accomplish in this "
"offensive. In real life, even though the initial advance had been "
"successful, the attacking force was too weak to push much further and the "
"strategic objectives were not met. This marked the last serious offensive of "
"the Wehrmacht in the east."
msgstr ""
"¡Bien hecho! Has logrado casi todo lo que había que habíamos puesto como "
"objetivo para esta ofensiva. En la operación histórica real, aunque el "
"avance inicial fué exitoso, las fuerzas alemanas fueron demasiado débiles "
"para avanzar lo suficiente, con lo que los objetivos estratégicos no se "
"cumplieron. Esta fue la última ofensiva seria de la Wehrmacht en el este."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Oh no! That ruins our chances to get to the strategic objectives - the oil "
"fields. This means the immediate end to our ambitions. It seems we should "
"have tried differently. "
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, no! Esto arruina nuestras posibilidades de llegar a los objetivos "
"estratégicos: los campos de petróleo. Esto significa el fin inmediato de "
"nuestras capacidad ofensiva en el este. Parece que deberíamos haberlo "
"intentado de otra manera"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/place"
msgid "6th Army"
msgstr "6º Ejército"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/reinf_crew"
msgid "Tankmen"
msgstr "Tanquistas"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/reinf_squad"
msgid "Panzergrenadiere"
msgstr "Panzergrenadiere"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/story"
msgid " On the eastern front, Budapest has been lost to the Soviets in February. The last Hungarian oil reserves available to the axis have also been lost. Hitler decides a counterattack must be conducted. General Balck and the resurrected 6th army are sent to the attack. His forces, among which the IIIrd Panzer Korps, will be part of a pincer attack into the area south- east of lake Balaton. The objective is to reach the Danube river. On march 6th, the main force attacks from the north side of Balaton.\n\n In this mission, you will be put in charge of the attack on the village of Sárszentágota. Your supply state is critical, and therefore your first objectives will be to take the Soviet fuel and supply dumps. Once you have resupplied your units, push on to take the enemy HQ in order to eliminate any threat of a counterattack. Use any enemy equipment you can capture and repair to make the odds a little bit less desperate.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"En el frente oriental, Budapest ha caído\n"
"\n"
"ante los soviéticos en febrero. Las últimas reservas de petróleo\n"
"\n"
"disponibles para el eje también se han perdido.\n"
"\n"
"Hitler decide que se debe realizar un contraataque\n"
"\n"
"El general Balck y el resucitado 6º ejército son enviados a\n"
"\n"
"al ataque. Sus fuerzas, entre las que se encuentra el IIIº Panzer Korps,\n"
"\n"
"formarán parte de un ataque en pinza hacia el\n"
"\n"
"área al sur-este del lago Balaton\n"
"\n"
"El objetivo es llegar al río Danubio\n"
"\n"
"El 6 de marzo, la fuerza principal ataca desde el lado norte\n"
"\n"
"de Balaton\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, estarás a cargo del ataque\n"
"\n"
"en el pueblo de Sárszentágota. Tus tropas están al límite\n"
"\n"
"de recursos, y por lo tanto tus primeros objetivos serán tomar\n"
"\n"
"los depósitos de combustible y suministros soviéticos. Despues,\n"
"\n"
"sigue adelante para tomar el cuartel general enemigo\n"
"\n"
"para eliminar cualquier amenaza de contraataque.\n"
"\n"
"Utiliza cualquier vehículo enemigo que puedas capturar y reparar para\n"
"\n"
"hacer que las probabilidades sean un poco menos desesperadas\n"
"\n"
"  \n"
"\n"
"Buena suerte."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task1"
msgid "Clear the crossroads for reinforcements to arrive."
msgstr "Despeja el cruce para que lleguen los refuerzos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task2"
msgid "Capture the ammo depot."
msgstr "Captura el depósito de municiones."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task3"
msgid "Capture the fuel depot."
msgstr "Captura el depósito de combustible."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task4"
msgid "Capture the repair workshop."
msgstr "Captura el taller de reparación."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task5"
msgid "Destroy the enemy HQ."
msgstr "Destruye el cuartel general enemigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task6"
msgid "Defend from the soviet assault, fall back to the original position."
msgstr "Defiéndete del asalto soviético, replegándote a la posición original."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task_sec"
msgid "Secret Objective"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/task_sec1"
msgid "Secret Objective: Salvage some of the soviet tanks in the swamp."
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto: Rescatar algunos de los tanques soviéticos en el pantano."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/timer"
msgid "The counterattack will arrive in:"
msgstr "El contraataque llegará en:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1945_03_spring-awakening/timer2"
msgid "Defend your starting position!"
msgstr "¡Defiende tu posición inicial!"
